Package: adSplit
Title: Annotation-Driven Clustering
Version: 1.9.0
Author: Claudio Lottaz, Joern Toedling
Description: This package implements clustering of microarray
	gene expression profiles according to functional 
	annotations. For each term genes are annotated to,
	splits into two subclasses are computed and a
	significance of the supporting gene set is determined.
Maintainer: Claudio Lottaz <claudio.lottaz@molgen.mpg.de>
Depends: R (>= 2.1.0), methods (>= 2.1.0), stats (>= 2.1.0), cluster (>= 1.9.1), multtest (>= 1.6.0),
	Biobase (>= 1.5.12), affy (>= 1.6.7), GO (>= 1.8.1), KEGG (>= 1.8.1)
Suggests: golubEsets (>= 1.0), vsn (>= 1.5.0), hu6800 (>= 1.8.1)
biocViews: Microarray, Statistics, Clustering
LazyLoad:	yes
URL: http://compdiag.molgen.mpg.de/software/index.shtml
License: GPL version 2.0 or newer


